ef"><span class="number">14.1.2 </span>User/relationship associations</a></li><li class="subsection"><a href="following_users_fragment.html#sec-relationship_validations" class="heading hyperref"><span class="number">14.1.3 </span>Relationship validations</a></li><li class="subsection"><a href="following_users_fragment.html#sec-following" class="heading hyperref"><span class="number">14.1.4 </span>Followed users</a></li><li class="subsection"><a href="following_users_fragment.html#sec-followers" class="heading hyperref"><span class="number">14.1.5 </span>Followers</a></li></ul></li><li class="section"><a href="following_users_fragment.html#sec-a_web_interface_for_following_and_followers" class="heading hyperref"><span class="number">14.2 </span>A web interface for following users</a></li><li><ul><li class="subsection"><a href="following_users_fragment.html#sec-sample_following_data" class="heading hyperref"><span class="number">14.2.1 </span>Sample following data</a></li><li class="subsection"><a href="following_users_fragment.html#sec-stats_and_a_follow_form" class="heading hyperref"><span class="number">14.2.2 </span>Stats and a follow form</a></li><li class="subsection"><a href="following_users_fragment.html#sec-following_and_followers_pages" class="heading hyperref"><span class="number">14.2.3 </span>Following and followers pages</a></li><li class="subsection"><a href="following_users_fragment.html#sec-a_working_follow_button_the_standard_way" class="heading hyperref"><span class="number">14.2.4 </span>A working follow button the standard way</a></li><li class="subsection"><a href="following_users_fragment.html#sec-a_working_follow_button_with_ajax" class="heading hyperref"><span class="number">14.2.5 </span>A working follow button with Ajax</a></li><li class="subsection"><a href="following_users_fragment.html#sec-following_tests" class="heading hyperref"><span class="number">14.2.6 </span>Following tests</a></li></ul></li><li class="section"><a href="following_u